{"tid":1059634,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【能力被調高】武磊超強表現征服《FIFA 19》","createTime":"2019-03-13T09:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T09:45:34.000Z","uid":173952,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f0f0103ac1ecb7aec30e88727cb6a57e5191b2c3","tid":1059634,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T09:03:34.000Z","msg":"武磊在西甲表現很出色<br />\n<br />\n  《FIFA 19》足球遊戲更新了球員能力值數據，愛斯賓奴的中國球星武磊能力值再次上調，達到了80。武磊的愛斯賓奴隊友伊格萊西亞斯的能力值為本週也是80。<br />\n<br />\n  此前武磊的綜合能力值為76，由於表現出色，武磊獲得了4分的周加成，能力值來到80。<br />\n<br />\n  需要指出的是，此前《FIFA 19》給武磊設定的綜合能力值只有76分，而這個分數對於一名第一次出國旅歐的中國球員來說已經不低了，要知道在意甲大殺四方的AC米蘭神鋒比亞迪克目前也只有76分的綜合評分。<br />\n<br />\n  目前五大聯賽中，能力值為80的前鋒有西維爾前鋒A席，里昂前鋒比比，愛華頓的巴西國腳理查利森。"},{"pid":"fcf07d6819fff6bc5e3a783bc87869c3e5121770","tid":1059634,"uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T09:06:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/cbNkHRcoCDk/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FcbNkHRcoCDk%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=8bc64393&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"633e58b134c8a0bb8f56833d51f308aada204e5b","tid":1059634,"uid":37303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T09:13:20.000Z","msg":"80咁撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217856c0c2796f3af0365296956416fc9d18db84","tid":1059634,"uid":226824,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T09:28:59.000Z","msg":"為左吸引班大陸仔買fifa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faabbbdca7d53285605935dd75fbf3322bdbff81","tid":1059634,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T09:30:49.000Z","msg":"冇女同李察利臣同level<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d97f11739b84dd4db098eb916048273f2472f30","tid":1059634,"uid":223534,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T09:31:25.000Z","msg":"真係cls 